{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d4c3ff3c21","title":"为爱晚亭题名","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"411a3a4297","index":0,"year":1952,"month":9,"day":null,"articleId":"d4c3ff3c21"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji32","name":"毛泽东全集第32卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/32-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji32":{"comments":[{"id":"c154564710","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"d4c3ff3c21","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"爱晚亭，位于岳麓山下清风峡中，亭坐西向东，三面环山。出岳麓书院后门，沿石径行200米，便是爱晚亭。清乾隆五十七年岳麓书院山长罗典创建。原名红叶亭，后湖广总督毕沉据唐代诗人杜牧《山行》“停车坐爱枫林晚”，改为爱晚亭。毛泽东青年时代，在第一师范求学，常与罗学、张昆弟等人一起到岳麓书院，与蔡和森聚会于爱晚亭下，纵谈时局，探求真理。因为这个缘故，1952年湖南大学重修爱晚亭时，校长李达致书毛泽东，请求题写亭名，毛泽东愉快地接受了请求。现在的爱晚亭亭遍，就是由毛泽东亲笔手书制成的。"}],"contents":[{"id":"f89fb29e1c","type":"title","text":"为爱晚亭题名”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"d4c3ff3c21"},{"id":"c154564710","type":"paragraph","text":"爱晚亭","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"d4c3ff3c21"}],"page":{"id":"8dfd6a0e46","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"d4c3ff3c21","start":249,"end":249}}}},"__N_SSG":true}